data.description: Dive right into your new POOL HOME!! 4 bedroom (or 3+ a den), 2-bathroom home with a NEW ROOF boasts a Massive Owners Suite, measuring an impressive 19' x 13', providing you the ultimate retreat.  New roof installed in 2022. Smart floor plan offers split bedrooms, family room, dining room, den, laundry room & eat in kitchen.  There are plenty of spaces from which to enjoy your beautifully landscaped yard- the screened pool area boasts a large area under truss and there is a screened front porch- perfect for catching the crossbreeze and not the bugs. Craving some sun? Recently repainted pool area provides ample room for basking by the stunning pool. Large kitchen features plenty of storage, island & a small work station. 2019 AC. Hurricane shutters protect the home, ensuring your comfort & peace of mind. If it is time for you to move into a slower pace, the beautiful Hawk's Preserve in E Ft Myers is the place to do it! Conveniently located 15 minutes from I-75, off Palm Beach Blvd, near grocers, in a community offering a playground, sidewalks & Low HOA fees this truley offers the best of both worlds. Schedule a showing today to call this affordable paradise w/ a spacious yard HOME.
